### 첫 번째 페이지 Product Comment 조회 (Product ID 입력 필요)
# 예시: GET {{baseUrl}}/products/YOUR_PRODUCT_ID/comments?take=5
GET http://localhost:3000/products/82c3b880-8f04-45f3-886c-a25f1749a7f0/comments?take=5

### 다음 페이지 Product Comment 조회 (Product ID와 이전 응답의 nextCursor 값 입력 필요)
# 예시: GET {{baseUrl}}/products/YOUR_PRODUCT_ID/comments?take=5&cursor=NEXT_CURSOR_VALUE
GET http://localhost:3000/products/82c3b880-8f04-45f3-886c-a25f1749a7f0/comments?take=5&cursor=99710df0-16bc-40f2-af0e-0aaa3483ba02

### 새 Product Comment 생성 (Product ID 입력 필요)
POST http://localhost:3000/products/82c3b880-8f04-45f3-886c-a25f1749a7f0/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "이 제품에 대한 첫 번째 댓글입니다!"
}

### 특정 Product Comment 조회 (Product ID, Comment ID 입력 필요)
GET http://localhost:3000/products/82c3b880-8f04-45f3-886c-a25f1749a7f0/comments/d85b6c16-3af8-4b7a-862d-93b5df446a0f

### Product Comment 업데이트 (Product ID, Comment ID 입력 필요)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/products/82c3b880-8f04-45f3-886c-a25f1749a7f0/comments/d85b6c16-3af8-4b7a-862d-93b5df446a0f
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "업데이트된 댓글 내용입니다."
}

### Product Comment 삭제 (Product ID, Comment ID 입력 필요)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/82c3b880-8f04-45f3-886c-a25f1749a7f0/comments/d85b6c16-3af8-4b7a-862d-93b5df446a0f